<!-- Definition and medical uses -->

'''克拉黴素'''（{{lang-en|Clarithromycin}}）也稱為'''甲紅黴素'''，[[商品|商品]]名為{{lang|en|Biaxin}}，是一種用來治療多種[[細菌|細菌]]感染的[[抗生素|抗生素]]，<ref name=AHFS2015>{{cite web|title=Vancocin|url=http://www.drugs.com/monograph/vancocin.html|publisher=The American Society of Health-System Pharmacists|accessdate=2015-09-04|archive-date=2015-09-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150906002445/http://www.drugs.com/monograph/vancocin.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>包括了[[鏈球菌性喉炎|鏈球菌性喉炎]]、[[肺炎|肺炎]]、皮膚感染、[[幽門螺旋桿菌|幽門螺旋桿菌]]感染、[[萊姆病|萊姆病]]等，大多是[[口服|口服]]藥物形式。<!-- <ref name=AHFS2015/> --><ref name=AHFS2015/>

<!-- Side effects and mechanism -->
常見副作用包括噁心、嘔吐、頭痛和腹瀉，罕見的情況是會出現[[嚴重過敏反應|嚴重過敏反應]]。<!-- <ref name=AHFS2015/> -->此药物可能會影響肝功能<!-- <ref name=AHFS2015/> -->，另外若于懷孕期間使用，可能存在用藥風險<!-- <ref name=AHFS2015/> -->。此藥物由[[紅黴素|紅黴素]]製成，化學稱為“6-O-甲基紅黴素”，<ref>{{cite book|last1=Kirst|first1=Herbert A.|title=Macrolide Antibiotics|date=2012|publisher=Birkhäuser Basel|location=Basel|isbn=9783034881050|page=53|edition=2|url=https://books.google.ca/books?id=8Vn2BwAAQBAJ&pg=PA53|access-date=2017-02-10|archive-date=2016-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305031148/https://books.google.ca/books?id=8Vn2BwAAQBAJ&pg=PA53|dead-url=no}}</ref>屬於[[巨環內酯|巨環內酯]]類，機轉是透過抑制某些細菌製造蛋白質達成。<ref name=AHFS2015/>

<!-- History, society and culture -->
克拉黴素是1980年代發明的，<ref>{{cite book|last1=Greenwood|first1=David|title=Antimicrobial drugs : chronicle of a twentieth century medical triumph|date=2008|publisher=Oxford University Press|location=Oxford|isbn=9780199534845|page=239|edition=1|url=https://books.google.ca/books?id=i4_FZHmzjzwC&pg=PA239|access-date=2017-02-10|archive-date=2019-12-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191208140945/https://books.google.ca/books?id=i4_FZHmzjzwC&pg=PA239|dead-url=no}}</ref> 它被列入[[世界卫生组织基本药物标准清单|世界卫生组织基本药物标准清单]]，是基礎衛生系統需要的重要藥物之一。<ref>{{cite web|title=WHO Model List of EssentialMedicines|url=http://apps.who.int/iris/bitstream/10665/93142/1/EML_18_eng.pdf?ua=1|work=World Health Organization|accessdate=22 April 2014|date=October 2013|archive-date=2016-04-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160411133939/http://apps.who.int/iris/bitstream/10665/93142/1/EML_18_eng.pdf?ua=1|dead-url=no}}</ref>它可作為一般用藥。<ref name=AHFS2015/>批發成本每劑介於0.13至0.79美元之間。<ref name=ERC2014>{{cite web|title=Clarithromycin|url=http://erc.msh.org/dmpguide/resultsdetail.cfm?language=english&code=CLA500T&s_year=2014&year=2014&str=500%20mg&desc=Clarithromycin&pack=new&frm=TAB-CAP&rte=PO&class_code2=06%2E2%2E2%2E&supplement=&class_name=%2806%2E2%2E2%2E%29Other%20antibacterials%3Cbr%3E|website=International Drug Price Indicator Guide|accessdate=7 September 2015}}{{dead link|date=2018年5月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>在美國，此藥中等偏貴，每療程約花費50至100美元。<ref name=Ric2015>{{cite book|last1=Hamilton|first1=Richart|title=Tarascon Pocket Pharmacopoeia 2015 Deluxe Lab-Coat Edition|date=2015|publisher=Jones & Bartlett Learning|isbn=9781284057560|page=92}}</ref>

